According to the spokesperson, the company has invested more than 5 million pounds in the Tollcross factory in recent years, especially in its production lines and in improving its operations.
“We are aware of Tollcross’s long history as a production facility and will be the first to tell employees and trade union representatives if we are to make changes to the factory’s operations.”
